# No API key needed by default: all models run through your LOCAL Claude Code
# install (Pro/Max subscription auth) via ai-sdk-provider-claude-code.
# Just make sure `claude` is installed and logged in.
#
# To switch back to the Anthropic API instead, set the key below and change
# the agents' `model:` back to the string 'anthropic/claude-sonnet-4-5'.
# ANTHROPIC_API_KEY=sk-ant-...
